/work-we-like/standing-tall-a-song-for-o.description: Desi Music Entertainment is a startup label that focuses on the promotion and distribution of music internationally for artists in India and the U.S. DME walks budding musicians through the basics of getting their music and brand out there and guides the artist through the extensive journey of music making: from inception to distribution and profit. We are a different kind of label. Artists can choose from one of our many packages, all of which include branding tutorials and concept creation, photo shoots, social media development, recording sessions, tracks mixed by industry professionals, mastering by Universal Mastering Studios and digital distribution through multiple digital giants.
